  "body": "Currently we quit the app when clicking on the \"x\" we should just close it and let it run. This is the expected behaviour on MacOS.\r\n<img width=\"324\" alt=\"Screen_Shot_2021-01-19_at_13_49_46\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105036843-618cae00-5a5d-11eb-89e1-2e0a1e305621.png\">\r\n\r\nCMD + W (Close window) shortcut is not working on MacOS. The expected behaviour is to close the app (not quit)\r\n\r\nSo when I click on \"x\" or hit CMD + W the app should close but still \"live\" the the app bar\r\n<img width=\"136\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-01-19 at 13 49 53\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/105037068-b29ca200-5a5d-11eb-8328-a1875babacad.png\">\r\n",
